Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:12.22,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be3}いつか　花咲く頃

Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:19.51,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}Blue  Yellow  Purple  Red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:23.29,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}叹息着的各种颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:31.16,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你给我的那些无法名状回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:36.86,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}我却一次次想起
